Welcome to the Climate Change Impact Analysis

Climate change is one of the most pressing challenges facing the planet today. This project aims to study and analyze the impacts of climate change, including rising temperatures, carbon emissions, and other environmental changes. By collecting and analyzing data, we provide insights that help make informed decisions in addressing this global crisis.
